snippet.textDisplay: Every musical decisionn during the production of this song went horribly wrong... except for the inclusion of Maithili Thakur. She saved the song from totally tanking. Ravi Kishan is not a musically gifted person, you should have taken Manoj Tiwari and had him participate more in the composition, instead of inserting rap. Also, culturally, you can talk about bhaang and music in the lyrics of a song about holi, but not botal/daru. never had such lapses in any previous seasons of coke studio. Expected much better!
